descriptions: You can download a trial version of this app to try it for 20 minutes for free.
You won’t be charged anything when this free trial ends. You can’t make in-app purchases or use add-on content during this free trial, but you’ll keep any achievements you earn.

display_long_description:
# Put your problem-solving skills to the test in Wet, a calming puzzle game. Play in mixed reality as you manipulate terrain and guide water to rescue the Rock Spirits.  
  
Be part of the WET community on Discord: https://discord.gg/XVrks3V9VZ
[media]

Raise and lower the land to create pathways and control where the water flows. Each puzzling challenge presents a unique test, forcing you to think creatively and strategically in the beautiful, calming landscape.  
  
Perfect for puzzle lovers with a creative streak, who enjoy a mix of tactile feedback and brain-teasing gameplay. Wet offers a relaxing yet stimulating puzzle experience.

[media]

# Features:

- 32 dynamic puzzles to challenge your mind
- Unique terrain manipulation mechanics
- Water flow simulation for complex problem-solving
- Beautiful, calming landscapes with soothing sounds
- Endless replayability; try to complete each puzzle in the fewest possible terrain moves

Get your problem-solving skills flowing, one puzzle at a time!

[media]
